00:20:37.000 --> 00:20:39.000
I think I'm fly fishing, Rick.

525
00:20:39.000 --> 00:20:43.000
You can distinguish me from the Rick that you had a falling out with by my fly fishing enthusiasm

526
00:20:43.000 --> 00:20:44.000
and accompanying hat.

527
00:20:44.000 --> 00:20:48.000
I hope I could be of service if you ever find the planet to be in danger.

528
00:20:48.000 --> 00:20:49.000
Friends?

529
00:20:51.000 --> 00:20:52.000
Sounds good to me.

530
00:20:53.000 --> 00:20:54.000
Kids, dinner!

531
00:20:54.000 --> 00:20:57.000
I got Panda Express. Did you get sugar chicken?

532
00:20:57.000 --> 00:20:58.000
That's kind of the only thing they have.

533
00:20:58.000 --> 00:21:00.000
I love Panda E. Thanks, Mom.

534
00:21:00.000 --> 00:21:03.000
I'm hoping to get a piece of your sugar chicken later.

535
00:21:03.000 --> 00:21:04.000
Stop it.

536
00:21:04.000 --> 00:21:07.000
There's your stupid hat, tiff shit.

537
00:21:07.000 --> 00:21:09.000
Dad, you can't talk to Jerry that way anymore.

538
00:21:09.000 --> 00:21:11.000
We're a real family now.

539
00:21:11.000 --> 00:21:14.000
In many ways, things will be like season one, but more streamlined.

540
00:21:14.000 --> 00:21:20.000
Now Jerry and I are happily married parents, and the idea that I was motivated by a fear of you leaving can be a shoot.

541
00:21:20.000 --> 00:21:22.000
A shoot? You've never used that word.

542
00:21:22.000 --> 00:21:24.000
Maybe you are a clone.

543
00:21:24.000 --> 00:21:26.000
It's not like Rick would tell us.

544
00:21:30.000 --> 00:21:31.000
No!

545
00:22:00.000 --> 00:22:05.000
Oh, we! What a season!

546
00:22:05.000 --> 00:22:08.000
Sorry I never showed up, but I got married.

547
00:22:08.000 --> 00:22:12.000
I had a baby. I went back to school and got my GED.

548
00:22:12.000 --> 00:22:15.000
What did you do while you were waiting?

549
00:22:15.000 --> 00:22:18.000
Hopefully you didn't just fuck around and waste your life.

550
00:22:18.000 --> 00:22:25.000
Oh, we! See you for season four in like a really long time.

551
00:22:25.000 --> 00:22:36.000
I might even have a big white Santa Claus beard and a couple of grandkids and all that kind of stuff.

552
00:22:36.000 --> 00:22:38.000
See you then!

553
00:22:40.000 --> 00:22:42.000
Oh my god!

554
00:22:42.000 --> 00:22:43.000
Did you get any of that?

